articles.title: Tuchel wants Chelsea coach Anthony Barry to join them at Bayern Munich - We Ain't Got No History
articles.content: Thomas Tuchel was appointed Bayern Munich head coach yesterday, and as usual, he will be accompanied by his long-time assistants Arno Michels and Zsolt Lw, both of whom left Chelsea* at the same time… [+2298 chars]
